Post-Match Reflections: Luka Dončić admitted he's not 100 percent healthy, promising he will be.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Dallas won the game, snapping a four-game losing streak and elevating them to 6-7.
Dončić had 16 points, 6 rebounds, and 6 assists, turning it over four times.
Dončić's performance was described as'mild, quiet, nearly inaudible.'
The game was a badly needed win for the Mavericks.
